Regression

Basic Model

\[ followback_i = \beta_0 + \beta_1 \cdot private_i + \beta_2 \cdot followingratio_i + \beta_3 \cdot followers_i + \epsilon_i\]

Basic Discontinuous Model

\[ followback_i = \beta_0 + \beta_1 \cdot private_i + \beta_2 \cdot followingratio_i + \beta_3 \cdot followers_i + \beta_4 \cdot [followingratio_i \geq 1] + \epsilon_i\]

Private-Interacted Discontinuous Model

\[ followback_i = \beta_0 + \beta_1 \cdot private_i + \beta_2 \cdot followingratio_i + \beta_3 \cdot followers_i + \\ \beta_4 \cdot [followingratio_i \geq 1] + \beta_5 \cdot [followingratio_i \geq 1] \cdot private_i + \epsilon_i\]
